graph LR
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    Dashboard -->|authentication| OAuth[OpenShift OAuth Server 4.x]
    Dashboard -->|resource management| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server 1.24+]
    Dashboard -->|external access| Route[OpenShift Route/Ingress 4.x]
    Dashboard -->|runtime| NodeJS[Node.js Runtime 18+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    Dashboard -.->|metrics queries| Prometheus[Prometheus 2.x]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies (CRD Read)
    Dashboard -->|read config| DSC[DataScienceCluster]
    Dashboard -->|check status| DSCI[DSCInitialization]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies (CRD CRUD)
    Dashboard -->|manage lifecycle| Notebooks[Kubeflow Notebooks]
    Dashboard -->|configure runtimes| KServe[KServe ServingRuntimes]
    Dashboard -->|manage instances| ModelRegistryCRD[ModelRegistry CR]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies (HTTP API)
    Dashboard -->|API calls| ModelRegistrySvc[Model Registry Service]
    Dashboard -->|pipeline ops| DSPipelines[Data Science Pipelines]
    Dashboard -->|bias metrics| TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service]

    %% Integration Points (Consume Dashboard)
    NotebookController[Kubeflow Notebook Controller] -.->|watches CRs| Dashboard
    KServeController[KServe Controller] -.->|watches CRs| Dashboard

    %% Custom Resources Managed
    Dashboard -->|creates/reads| AcceleratorProfile[AcceleratorProfile CR]
    Dashboard -->|reads| OdhApplication[OdhApplication CR]
    Dashboard -->|manages| OdhDashboardConfig[OdhDashboardConfig CR]
    Dashboard -->|reads| OdhDocument[OdhDocument CR]
    Dashboard -->|reads| OdhQuickStart[OdhQuickStart CR]

    %% Styling
    style Dashboard fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External Dependencies
    style OAuth fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Route fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style NodeJS fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Prometheus fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5,color:#fff

    %% Internal ODH Components
    style DSC fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style DSCI fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style Notebooks fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style KServe fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style ModelRegistryCRD fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style ModelRegistrySvc fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style DSPipelines fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style TrustyAI fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style NotebookController fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5,color:#000
    style KServeController fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5,color:#000

    %% Custom Resources
    style AcceleratorProfile fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style OdhApplication fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#000
